OL,5,G0245 Four in a Bed
OL,6,     FThe competition kicks off at the
OL,7,     F'self B&B' Bove Town House in
OL,8,     FGlastonbury, where Shannon
OL,9,     FSlater-Dent and Trevor Tredgett
OL,10,     Ftreat their guests to an afternoon
OL,11,     Fof group sound healing.
OL,12,G0310 Four in a Bed
OL,13,     FKathryn Langley and Trevor Burnell
OL,14,     Fwelcome their rivals to Treberthan
OL,15,     FB&B in Cornwall, where they nearly
OL,16,     Fcome unstuck at breakfast and are
OL,17,     Fleft with some explaining to do.
