OL,5,G0430 Four in a Bed
OL,6,     FIt's the final day and the B&Bers
OL,7,     Fmeet for the last time to find out
OL,8,     Fhow much they've been paid.
OL,9,     FTensions run high as issues of
OL,10,     Fhygiene, noise and delayed
OL,11,     Fbreakfasts are raised.
OL,12,G0455 Couples Come Dine with Me
OL,13,     FIn Leeds, the competition features
OL,14,     Fa Pavarotti-style vocal
OL,15,     Fperformance, home-cooked fare and
OL,16,     Ffine dining, a problem preparing
OL,17,     Fduck to order, and a mankini...
OL,18,G0550 The King of Queens
OL,19,     FSandwiched Out: Doug's jealous
OL,20,     Fwhen Deacon has a sandwich named
OL,21,     Fafter him. Guest starring Neil
OL,22,     FSedaka as himself.
